_:N6c5cb9a01060401f92fcf1a49874194c <http://schema.org/text> "The Defence Infrastructure Organisation (DIO) is the estate expert for defence, supporting the armed forces to enable military capability by planning, building, maintaining, and servicing infrastructure." <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
